{
  "texts": [
    "The second hybridization event happened between a domesticated tetraploid wheat and the D genome progenitor Tausch's goatgrass (Ae.",
    "tauschii; 2n = 2x = 14, DD genome).",
    "This hybridization that gave rise to bread wheat most probably occurred along the southern shores of the Caspian Sea 8,000-11,000 years ago 5, 6.",
    "To comprehensively assess genetic diversity in Ae.",
    "tauschii, we first compiled a presence-absence k-mer matrix from a diversity panel comprising 920 sequenced Ae."
  ]
}